 "text_old": "{{pp-blp|small=yes}}\n{{short description|Thai actor}}\n{{Infobox person\n| name               = Metawin Opas-iamkajorn\n| image              = Winmetawin.jpg\n| alt                = \n| caption            = \n| birth_name         = \n| native_name        = \u0e40\u0e21\u0e18\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19 \u0e42\u0e2d\u0e20\u0e32\u0e2a\u0e40\u0e2d\u0e35\u0e48\u0e22\u0e21\u0e02\u0e08\u0e23\n| native_name_lang   = tha\n| birth_date         = {{Birth date and age|1999|02|21}}\n| birth_place        = [[Bangkok]], [[Thailand]]\n| alma_mater         = \n| height             = {{height|ft=6|in=0.7}}\n| other_names        = Win\n| occupation         = [[Actor]]\n| years_active       = 2019\u2013present\n| notable_works      = {{plainlist|\n*Tine in ''[[2gether: The Series (Thai TV series)|2gether: The Series]]''\n}}\n| agent              = [[GMMTV]]\n| website            = \n}}\n\n'''Metawin Opas-iamkajorn''' ({{lang-th|\u0e40\u0e21\u0e18\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19 \u0e42\u0e2d\u0e20\u0e32\u0e2a\u0e40\u0e2d\u0e35\u0e48\u0e22\u0e21\u0e02\u0e08\u0e23}}; also known as '''Win''' ({{lang-th|\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19}}), born February 21, 1999) is a [[Thailand|Thai]] actor. He is known for his main role as ''Tine'' in [[GMMTV]]'s ''[[2gether: The Series (Thai TV series)|2gether: The Series]]'' (2020) where he stars as [[Vachirawit Chiva-aree]]'s love interest.<ref>{{cite web |title=Biodata Aktor Thailand Win Metawin Opa-iamkajorn |url=https://dianiopiari.com/biodata-aktor-thailand-win-metawin-opas-iamkajorn/ |website=dianiopiari.com |publisher=Diani Opiari |accessdate=20 March 2020 |language=Indonesian |date=16 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=\"\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19\" \u0e15\u0e35\u0e1a\u0e17\u0e41\u0e15\u0e01\u0e0b\u0e35\u0e23\u0e35\u0e2a\u0e4c\u0e40\u0e23\u0e37\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e41\u0e23\u0e01 \u0e41\u0e1f\u0e19\u0e46 \u0e40\u0e2d\u0e47\u0e19\u0e14\u0e39\u0e15\u0e34\u0e14\u0e41\u0e2e\u0e0a\u0e41\u0e17\u0e47\u0e01 #\u0e17\u0e35\u0e21\u0e41\u0e21\u0e48\u0e44\u0e17\u0e19\u0e4c \u0e43\u0e19 \"\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e23\u0e32\u0e30\u0e40\u0e23\u0e32\u0e04\u0e39\u0e48\u0e01\u0e31\u0e19\" |url=https://www.sanook.com/movie/96441/ |website=sanook.com |publisher=Sanook |accessdate=20 March 2020 |language=Thai |date=20 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Early life and education==\nMetawin was born in Bangkok, Thailand. He completed his secondary education in Panyarat High School where he had the opportunity to become an exchange student in [[Belmond-Klemme Community School District]] at [[Iowa]], [[United States]].<ref>{{cite web |title= #FantalkwithWin|url=https://twitter.com/winmetawin/status/1244628358228365315 |website=twitter.com |publisher=@winmetawin |accessdate=31 March 2020}}</ref> He became a member of the percussion choir in Belmond-Klemme High School band, where his group received a Superior rating.<ref>{{cite web |title= Musicians get lots of 'ones'|url=http://www.belmondnews.com/news/musicians-get-lots-of-ones/article_808c1cb8-b7a9-540d-802e-eb040d634a79.html|website=belmondnews.com |publisher= The Belmond Independent |accessdate=16 April 2020 |language=English |date= 14 April 2016}}</ref> He also passed the [[General Educational Development]] (GED) examination upon his graudation. Win is currently taking up Economics (International Program) in [[Thammasat University]].<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0e2a\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e1b\u0e23\u0e30\u0e27\u0e31\u0e15\u0e34 \"\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19 \u0e40\u0e21\u0e18\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19\" \u0e2b\u0e23\u0e37\u0e2d \"\u0e44\u0e17\u0e19\u0e4c\" \u0e43\u0e19 \"\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e23\u0e32\u0e30\u0e40\u0e23\u0e32\u0e04\u0e39\u0e48\u0e01\u0e31\u0e19\" |url=https://www.daradaily.com/news/89519/read |website=daradaily.com |publisher=Daradaily |accessdate=20 March 2020 |language=Thai |date=20 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title=\u0e1b\u0e23\u0e30\u0e27\u0e31\u0e15\u0e34 \"\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19 \u0e40\u0e21\u0e18\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19\" \u0e19\u0e31\u0e01\u0e41\u0e2a\u0e14\u0e07\u0e14\u0e32\u0e27\u0e23\u0e38\u0e48\u0e07\u0e2b\u0e19\u0e38\u0e48\u0e21\u0e2b\u0e25\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e04\u0e27\u0e32\u0e21\u0e2a\u0e39\u0e07 185 \u0e0b\u0e21. \u0e08\u0e32\u0e01\u0e23\u0e31\u0e49\u0e27\u0e18\u0e23\u0e23\u0e21\u0e28\u0e32\u0e2a\u0e15\u0e23\u0e4c\u0e2d\u0e34\u0e19\u0e40\u0e15\u0e2d\u0e23\u0e4c |url=https://www.sanook.com/campus/1399827/ |website=sanook.com |publisher=Sanook |accessdate=31 March 2020 |language=Thai |date=25 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Career==\nMetawin made his acting debut with a main role as ''Tine'' in the ''[[2gether: The Series (Thai TV series)|2gether: The Series]]'' in 2019, a [[romance film|romantic]] [[comedy-drama]] [[television series]] produced by [[GMMTV]].<ref>{{cite web |title=\u0e2a\u0e48\u0e2d\u0e07\u0e1b\u0e23\u0e30\u0e27\u0e31\u0e15\u0e34 \"\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19 \u0e40\u0e21\u0e18\u0e27\u0e34\u0e19\" \u0e2b\u0e23\u0e37\u0e2d \"\u0e44\u0e17\u0e19\u0e4c\" \u0e43\u0e19 \"\u0e40\u0e1e\u0e23\u0e32\u0e30\u0e40\u0e23\u0e32\u0e04\u0e39\u0e48\u0e01\u0e31\u0e19\" |url=https://www.daradaily.com/news/89519/read |website=daradaily.com |publisher=Daradaily |accessdate=20 March 2020 |language=Thai |date=20 March 2020}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |title='2Gether': Here's everything to know about the Thai boy love show |url=https://filmdaily.co/news/2gether/|website=filmdaily.co |publisher=Film Daily |accessdate=16 April 2020 |language=English}}</ref> He has also starred as a guest on several [[GMMTV]] shows such as [[School Rangers]] and [[Talk with Toey]].\n\n==Personal life==\nIn his Twitter interaction with fans, he revealed that his favorite soccer player is [[FC Barcelona|Futbol Club Barcelona]]'s forward, [[Lionel Messi]].<ref>{{cite web |title= #FantalkwithWin|url=https://twitter.com/winmetawin/status/1244627082744713216 |website=twitter.com |publisher=@winmetawin |accessdate=31 March 2020}}</ref>\n\n==Filmography==\n===Television===\n{| class=\"wikitable\"\n! Year\n! Title\n! Role\n! Notes\n! Ref\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" style=\"text-align: center;\" | 2020\n| style=\"font-style:italic;\" | [[2gether: The Series