or]]''\n| Jimmy Horn\n|\n|-\n| 1994\n| ''Jackaboy Blue''\n| Guggles McMillian\n|\n|-\n| 1995\n| ''[[Tommy Boy (film)|Tommy Boy]]''\n| Big Tom Callahan II\n|\n|-\n| 1995\n| ''[[The Stars Fell on Henrietta]]''\n| Big Dave McDermot\n|\n|-\n| 1996\n| ''[[Romeo + Juliet]]''\n| Ted Montague\n|\n|-\n| 1999\n| ''[[The Virtuoso]]''\n| Unknown\n|\n|-\n| 1999\n| ''Out of the Cold''\n| David Bards\n|\n|-\n| 1999\n| ''Silicon Towers''\n| Tom Warner\n|\n|-\n| 2000\n| ''[[Dish Dogs]]''\n| Frost\n|\n|-\n| 2001\n| ''[[Summer Catch]]''\n| John Schiffner\n|\n|-\n| 2002\n| ''[[Stolen Summer]]''\n| Father Kelly\n|\n|-\n| 2002\n| ''Code Yellow: Hospital at Ground Zero''\n| Narrator\n|\n|-\n| 2002\n| ''Drawing First Blood''\n| Himself\n| Short\n|-\n| 2004\n| ''[[She Hate Me]]''\n| Chairman Billy Church\n|\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[Assault on Precinct 13 (2005 film)|Assault on Precinct 13]]''\n| Jasper O'Shea\n|\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''Tommy Boy: Behind the Laughter''\n| Himself\n| Short\n|-\n| 2005\n| ''[[10th and Wolf]]''\n| Agent Horvath\n|\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[Everyone's Hero]]''\n| Babe Ruth\n| Voice\n|-\n| 2006\n| ''[[The Ultimate Gift]]''\n| Gus\n|\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[Ratatouille (film)|Ratatouille]]''\n| Django\n| Voice\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''Welcome to Paradise''\n| Bobby Brown\n|\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''[[War Eagle, Arkansas (film)|War Eagle, Arkansas]]''\n| Pop\n|\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''Cat City''\n| Harold Vogessor\n|\n|-\n| 2008\n| ''[[Righteous Kill]]''\n| Lt. Hingus\n|\n|-\n| 2009\n| ''Factory 9''\n| Unknown\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Every Day (2010 film)|Every Day]]''\n| Ernie\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Meet Monica Velour]]''\n| Pop Pop\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[The Next Three Days]]''\n| George Brennan\n|\n|-\n| 2010\n| ''[[Alleged (film)|Alleged]]''\n| Clarence Darrow\n|\n|-\n| 2011\n| ''[[The Big Year]]''\n| Raymond Harris\n|\n|-\n| 2012\n| ''Twelfth Night''\n| Sir Toby Belch\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[The Challenger]]''\n| Chairman William Rogers\n|\n|-\n| 2015\n| ''[[Knight of Cups (film)|Knight of Cups]]''\n| Joseph\n|\n